### **🚀 Automated Error Pattern Application Engine**

**Revolutionary Pattern Recognition and Resolution System:**
```elixir
defmodule ErrorPatternEngine do
  @moduledoc """
  Automated error pattern detection and resolution system
  implementing TPS methodology with 5-Level RCA integration.
  """
  
  @patterns [
    {:ep041, ~r/missing.*end/, &fix_missing_end_statements/1},
    {:ep042, ~r/incomplete.*pattern/, &complete_pattern_matching/1}, 
    {:ep043, ~r/container.*dependency/, &add_container_validation/1},
    {:ep044, ~r/resource.*conflict/, &implement_coordination/1},
    {:ep045, ~r/dependency.*missing/, &add_dependency_checks/1},
    {:ep046, ~r/quality.*gap/, &standardize_error_handling/1},
    {:ep047, ~r/tps.*integration/, &enhance_tps_methodology/1},
    {:ep048, ~r/container.*compliance/, &validate_container_architecture/1},
    {:ep049, ~r/performance.*infrastructure/, &setup_performance_testing/1},
    {:ep050, ~r/documentation.*enhancement/, &improve_documentation/1},
    {:ep071, ~r/e2e.*testing/, &implement_wallaby_framework/1},
    {:ep072, ~r/traffic.*simulation/, &setup_load_testing/1},
    {:ep073, ~r/script.*quality/, &implement_quality_verification/1},
    {:ep074, ~r/browser.*automation/, &setup_progressive_scaling/1},
    {:ep075, ~r/cross.*browser/, &implement_compatibility_testing/1},
    {:ep076, ~r/mobile.*responsive/, &setup_mobile_testing/1},
    {:ep077, ~r/load.*performance/, &implement_dynamic_thresholds/1},
    {:ep078, ~r/documentation.*quality/, &setup_doc_assessment/1},
    {:ep079, ~r/agent.*coordination/, &optimize_efficiency/1},
    {:ep080, ~r/testing.*integration/, &implement_unified_framework/1}
  ]
  
  def apply_pattern_fixes(file_path) do
    # Systematic pattern application with TPS methodology
    # Implements Jidoka (stop and fix) when patterns detected
    Enum.reduce(@patterns, file_path, fn {pattern_id, regex, fix_func}, acc ->
      if pattern_detected?(acc, regex) do
        apply_5_level_rca(pattern_id, acc)
        fix_func.(acc)
      else
        acc
      end
    end)
  end
  
  defp apply_5_level_rca(pattern_id, context) do
    # Toyota Production System 5-Level Root Cause Analysis
    # Level 1: What happened? (symptom identification)
    # Level 2: Why did it happen? (surface cause)  
    # Level 3: Why did that cause occur? (underlying system behavior)
    # Level 4: Why wasn't it prevented? (configuration/implementation gaps)
    # Level 5: Why didn't our processes catch this? (design/requirements analysis)
  end
end
```

