### **🎯 PCIS Development Commands (MANDATORY WITH PHICS)**

#### **Daily Development Workflow with PHICS Integration**
```bash
# 1. Start PCIS development session with PHICS enabled
elixir scripts/pcis/development_workflow.exs --start development --enable-phics

# 2. PHICS container setup with hot-reloading
elixir scripts/pcis/containers/setup_phoenix_container.exs --enable-phics --claude-integration

# 3. Interactive development mode (RECOMMENDED)
elixir scripts/pcis/development_workflow.exs --interactive --phics-mode

# 4. PHICS compliance validation
elixir scripts/pcis/validation_cli.exs --phics-compliance --all

# 5. Domain-specific compilation with container hot-reloading
podman exec intelitor-dev elixir scripts/pcis/development_workflow.exs --compile [DOMAIN_NAME]

# 6. Comprehensive testing with PHICS integration
elixir scripts/testing/comprehensive_pcis_test_suite.exs --comprehensive --phics-enabled

# 7. Validation and compliance checking
elixir scripts/pcis/validation_cli.exs --all --container-compliance

# 8. Development status monitoring with container health
elixir scripts/pcis/development_workflow.exs --status --phics-health
```

